str(raw_df)

# 데이터 형변환
df <- raw_df
df$reg_dt <- as.POSIXct(df$reg_dt)

df <- as_tbl_time(df, index = reg_dt)
df <- df %>% group_by(spce_id)

이상 탐지

# anomalized 
df_anomalized <- df %>%
  time_decompose(tag_value, merge=TRUE) %>%
  anomalize(remainder,alpha = 0.05, max_anoms = 0.2) %>%
  time_recompose()
